---
import Base from "../../../layouts/Base.astro";
import Nav from "../../../components/Nav.astro";
import Footer from "../../../components/Footer.astro";
const title = "Hourwell — Privacy | DYNNI";
const description = "Privacy policy for Hourwell, an iOS app for time and earnings tracking for Norwegian TV/film freelancers.";
const canonical = "https://dynni.no/en/hourwell/privacy";
---
<Base lang="en" title={title} description={description} canonical={canonical}>
  <link slot="head" rel="stylesheet" href="/css/legal.css" />
  <Nav lang="en" />
  <main class="privacy-content">
      <h1>Hourwell — Privacy</h1>
      <p class="last-updated">Last updated: 9 May 2026</p>

      <p>Hourwell is an iOS app that helps freelancers in TV and film track their hours, calculate Norwegian collective-agreement supplements, send invoices, and compare rates anonymously. Privacy is built into the design — we collect as little as possible, and store as much as possible locally on your device.</p>

      <h2>What data Hourwell handles</h2>

      <h3>1. On your device</h3>
      <p>The following stays on your iPhone and iPad (synced via your own iCloud, never our servers):</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Time entries, projects, clients, invoices, expenses</li>
        <li>User preferences (currency, language, default rate, notification settings)</li>
        <li>Notes, photos attached to entries</li>
        <li>Geofence coordinates for projects (if you enable Smart auto-track)</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We have no access to this data. Delete the app and disable iCloud, and it's all gone.</p>

      <h3>2. Anonymous rate submissions (optional opt-in)</h3>
      <p>If you explicitly opt in, you can send anonymous rate data to the Community Rates feature. We send:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Production type (e.g. "Feature film")</li>
        <li>Role and seniority (e.g. "Cinematographer/DOP, 6 years")</li>
        <li>Day rate / hourly rate</li>
        <li>Year of the engagement</li>
        <li>A randomly generated <code>app_install_id</code> (UUID) used only for rate limiting</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We do <em>not</em> send your name, email, phone, project names, client names, or anything that could identify you. Data is hosted by Supabase (EU North region, GDPR-compliant). Aggregated statistics are hidden until at least 3 people have submitted for the same role and seniority (k-anonymity).</p>

      <h3>3. Permissions the app requests</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Microphone and Speech Recognition</strong>: Only when you actively use the "Voice entry" feature to log hours by voice. Audio is processed locally on iOS.</li>
        <li><strong>Location</strong>: Only if you enable "Smart auto-track" for a project. Uses Apple's geofence APIs; coordinates never leave your device.</li>
        <li><strong>Notifications</strong>: For long-shift reminders (over 10 hours), daily check-ins, and geofence prompts. You can disable these in Settings any time.</li>
        <li><strong>Photos</strong>: Only when you actively choose to attach a photo to an entry (e.g. for documentation).</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Third parties</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Apple iCloud</strong>: We use Apple's CloudKit for syncing between your own devices. Apple's privacy policy applies to that data.</li>
        <li><strong>Supabase</strong>: Only for anonymous rate submissions (opt-in). Server in EU North (Stockholm), GDPR-compliant.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We <em>never</em> sell data, we <em>never</em> share data with marketing companies, and we don't track you across apps.</p>

      <h2>Your rights</h2>
      <p>Under GDPR you have the right to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Access what data Hourwell holds about you (answer: nothing on our servers besides anonymous rate submissions)</li>
        <li>Have data deleted — uninstall the app, or email us if you want your anonymous app_install_id reset</li>
        <li>File a complaint with the Norwegian Data Protection Authority if you think we're mishandling data</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
      <p>If we make material changes, we'll notify you in the app. Minor edits (clarifications, corrections) are made directly on this page.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions or concerns? Email <a href="mailto:paal@dynni.no">paal@dynni.no</a>.</p>

      <p class="lang-toggle"><a href="/hourwell/privacy">Norsk versjon</a></p>
    </main>
  <Footer lang="en" />
</Base>
